summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 69W page 165 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 12-21 incl., Block 8, Lots 9-18 incl., Block 9, Lots 13-24 incl., Block 17, Lots 1-12 incl., Block 16, all in High Point Add. located on both sides of 34th Ave. S.W. from line 1 lot south of W. Graham St. to W. Holly St., from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
